Class MolString

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.chem.MolString

    public final class MolString
extends Object
implements ChemConstants, DispOptConsts, MechSynthConstants
    Holds molecule format interconversions and manipulations of graphical objects in MRV documents.
